# Intentionally (almost) empty.
#
# The vitest workers pool loads .dev.vars on top of [env.test.vars] from
# wrangler.toml. With decrypted secrets present, that repoints
# TINYBIRD_INGEST_URL at the real staging workspace, bypassing the fetch mock
# (shared/test/mocks/tinybird.ts intercepts localhost:7181 only) — so "mocked"
# tests silently read live staging data.
#
# This file shadows .dev.vars for the `test` environment, keeping unit tests
# on the mocked wrangler.toml [env.test.vars] values regardless of whether
# `npm run decrypt-vars` has been run.
